data.description: Welcome to a place where pride of ownership shines through every corner. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home on .67 acres is situated on a corner lot, with an open floor plan, strategically placed can lighting throughout the home, a separate family, and living room, the master bathroom features a garden tub, dual sinks for convenience, and a shower stall. This home is both functional and aesthetically pleasing. The kitchen has ample cabinets for storage, breakfast bar, stainless-steel appliances, including a refrigerator that stays with the home adds a modern touch to the space, the detached garage adds convenience for cars or for extra storage space.
